# Create AWS ECR Repository

```
aws ecr create-repository \
--repository-name devops-demo \
--region ap-south-1
```

Login to ECR:

```
aws ecr get-login-password \
--region ap-south-1 | docker login \
--username AWS \
--password-stdin <AWS_ACCOUNT_ID>.dkr.ecr.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com
```

